data.description:
90 percent brick.  2 car garage.

Neighborhood Description

Sub division gated lit tennis courts and pool.  There are two entrances to sub division.  Waterfall is in one entrance and second entrance has a pond on each side.  Home owners association, security, and party room available to sub division community.
data.whatILove: Great view on top of a hill.  Suburb of San Antonio.  Home Owners Association. Minutes from Fort Sam Houston Army Base and Randolph AFB.  Spacious master bedroom and bathroom with walk in closet.  Extra room with french doors - can be used as den or as a 4th bedroom.  Big back yard.  All the city amenities with NO CITY TAXES!  Live in county - 1 block from Converse and San Antonio, TX.
